data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bed, 2-bath home boasting 1584 SQFT of comfortable living space. Step inside and discover a freshly painted interior that exudes warmth and character. Convenience is at your fingertips with parking available in the basement garage, complete with walk-out access. You'll immediately notice the custom stone work on the front porch and gable, adding a touch of elegance to the facade. Inside, the Master Bedroom offers his and hers closets, ensuring ample storage for your belongings. The durable metal roof provides peace of mind for years to come, and the use of natural gas for heating adds efficiency to your everyday life. LVL, Vinyl, and Tile floors in home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely home your own. Located in a great neighborhood, you'll be only 2 mins to Downtown Sparta, 25 mins to Cookeville, & 1.5 hours to BNA! What are you waiting for? Schedule a viewing today!
